body:
#### PR description:

This PR contains only an update of the comments about the ETROC TDC window parameters (_tdcWindowStart_, _tdcWindowEnd_) in [mtdDigitizer_cfg.py](https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/compare/master...martinamalberti:mm_ETLDigi_updatedComment?expand=1#diff-95634aed61c8af87d99157184e029b89f721b151805ad859430447fedf2490a0R80-R81), for more clarity and future reference. The code itself is untouched.

#### PR validation:
The code compiles.
title: ETL digitization: update comments on TDC window parameters
